name: search_contacts
description: Search for contacts or places using a query.
parameters: {'search_query': 'What is the name or place you want to search for?'}

name: start_voice_search
description: Initiate a voice search for contacts or places.

name: open_dialpad
description: Open the dialpad to enter a phone number manually.

name: select_tab
description: Switch to a specific tab in the navigation bar.
parameters: {'tab_name': 'Which tab do you want to select? [Favorites, Recents, Contacts, Voicemail]'}

name: call_contact
description: Call a selected contact from the list.
parameters: {'contact_name': 'Whose contact do you want to call?'}
